            <div class="col-md-4 featured__col">
                <h2><span class="ssb-responsive"></span> Responsive</h2>
                <p>Simple Share Buttons Plus comes with 11 different button sets, all of which scale perfectly for mobile devices</p>
                <h2><span class="ssb-colorpicker"></span> Customise</h2>
                <p>Choose custom colour buttons and icons, including their hover colours using the built-in colourpicker functionality</p>
                <h2><span class="ssb-scissors"></span> URL Shortener</h2>
                <p>Shorten URLs with exclusive access to the <a href="http://ort.sh">ort.sh</a> URL shortener API, or use bit.ly</p>
            </div><!--
