            --><div class="col-md-4 featured__col">
                <h2><span class="ssb-tags"></span></span> Share Tags</h2>
                <p>Pick and choose the image, title and description that are selected when people share your content</p>
                <h2><span class="ssb-click"></span> Click Tracking</h2>
                <p>All share button events are tracked and can be seen in your tracking dashboard, including GeoIP information</p>
                <h2><span class="ssb-code"></span> Shortcodes</h2>
                <p>Add share buttons exactly where you want to using <code>[ssbp]</code>, or hide them using <code>[ssbp_hide]</code></p>
            </div>
